        <item>
            <title>【TGA 2024】《法環》平行世界新作公佈，《艾爾登法環，黑夜君臨》採用全新設計協力型玩法</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/13/elden-ring-nightreign/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=elden-ring-nightreign</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/13/elden-ring-nightreign/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 11:30:30 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[TGA 2024]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[艾爾登法環]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[艾爾登法環，黑夜君臨]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1281302</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>大受歡迎的《艾爾登法環》(Elden Ring) 不論原作和 DLC 都獲得很高的評價，今日 FromSoftware 就宣佈將會推出衍生作品《艾爾登法環，黑夜君臨》，以平行世界為設定，採用協力生存型玩法。<br /><span id="more-1281302"></span></p><p>今次公佈的新作《艾爾登法環，黑夜君臨》(Elden Ring Nightreign) 是與《艾爾登法環》獨立的遊戲新作，由《黑暗靈魂》系列資深開發者石崎淳也擔任監督而不是原作的宮崎英高。遊戲與原作世界觀相同，沿用部分來自原作的敵人及武器，不過設定上就不是同一時間線而是平行世界，因此不會影響原作故事內容。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_78076"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/K2DyEf0V-Vw?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>新作不同於原作的動作 RPG 玩法，採用協力生存遊戲玩法，支援單人或三人遊玩，比起故事更強調戰鬥體驗。玩家需選擇不同職業的「渡夜者」角色，在遊戲內的三日時間內，在隨機地形中探索、成長並對抗強敵。每個角色都擁有獨特的「技藝」和「絕活」，如使用特殊匕首或召喚巨大墓碑等能力，提供不同的戰術變化。玩家需要在不斷縮小的範圍內探索、獲取裝備和符文經驗，面對一波波的敵人生存三日，然後合力擊敗最後的「黑夜王」。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281319" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/03-8-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/03-8-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/03-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/04-8-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/04-8-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/04-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281321" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/05-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/05-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/05-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>遊戲將會在 2025 年全球同步推出，支援 PlayStation 5／PlayStation 4／Xbox Series X|S／Xbox One／STEAM 平台，有興趣的朋友不妨繼續留意進一步的公佈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281323" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/07-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/07-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/07.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281324" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/08-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/08-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/08.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>來源：新聞稿</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
