        <item>
            <title>香港的士車隊推 6 座電動的士，用 App 預約 + 預先電子付款 + 全車攝錄系統</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/13/syncab-6-seat-taxi-availabe-today/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=syncab-6-seat-taxi-availabe-today</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/13/syncab-6-seat-taxi-availabe-today/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 06:00:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[星羣的士]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[的士]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[純電動車]]>
